N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4205.10 - Copy of rules

State Regulations

Copies of the New York State Quarter Horse Racing

Commission rules and regulations shall be available at the commission office
and copies thereof shall be available at the quarter horse race tracks duly
licensed by the commission. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9

4205.10

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
